{"tid":1664024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選香港十大最可恥職業","createTime":"2019-10-19T19:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T20:51:17.000Z","uid":121213,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"95d46d74224e5411af720ccfff16d754bc5ce361","tid":1664024,"uid":121213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:23:30.000Z","msg":"有個post話九把刀問有咩職業係可恥 d網民就一面倒話香港警察<br />\n個post係有d小學雞，咁我就想做個民調睇下大家有咩提議<br />\n但唯一有個條件，要係合法職業<br />\n如有d狗也不屌的職業都可以講但要解釋點解可恥<br />\n1，各級警察(相信無異議啦）<br />\n2，特首及高官各級司局長<br />\n3，建制派議員<br />\n4，地產商<br />\n5，鄉事局班管理層<br />\n6，選舉主任<br />\n7，美心集團董事及管理層<br />\n8，黨鐵董事及管理層<br />\n9，無線及新聞部門<br />\n10，vtc高層<br />\n11，五毛黨<br />\n排名第一就越可恥 歡迎各位修改同提出議見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong>"},{"pid":"2617bd309d817c0e2ff7a7d48f9a60fd30a6e9cc","tid":1664024,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:23:48.000Z","msg":"[1020 行動Post] 香港人真係好痴線！不論組織力、耐力、創意玩到咁！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eovgRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eovgRS</a>"},{"pid":"50e31e72a6e225cbb91e58098b2af7d9475d54bf","tid":1664024,"uid":105924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:25:27.000Z","msg":"保險呢"},{"pid":"04096ab380ee687af21bcea5eb401597f221d632","tid":1664024,"uid":27146,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:31:56.000Z","msg":"黨鐵十甲不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5a0ed25364eeba84640c3a30e5ff9b119e01bc","tid":1664024,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:48:52.000Z","msg":"健身狗 倫敦金都無?"},{"pid":"adf6f95c3d310bfe4c0afa07e0a6eb44b4006680","tid":1664024,"uid":273353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:50:05.000Z","msg":"美咩心姐直接中資啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d8031ee19bee51541a4c796937dd28fffb3975","tid":1664024,"uid":104128,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedB